            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-04-15T12:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-01-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="21" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d21">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the position of the United States regarding the proposal of the
                    Secretary-General for the establishment of a United Nations security guard, with
                    reference to consideration of the matter by the General Assembly at the second
                    part of its third regular session in April 1949, see editorial note in <ref target="frus1948v01p1#pg_33">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1948, volume I, page 33</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
